(178, 14, 'content', 'Nebula Gaming was born in 2024, not in a high-rise corporate office, but from the bedroom of a passionate gamer in the Netherlands — me, Finn Siepers. At just 19 years old, I took the leap from being a lifelong fan of competitive gaming to becoming a founder. I grew up watching some of the biggest names in eSports dominate the world stage, studying their playstyles, their teamwork, their rise. I didn’t just admire them — I wanted to be one of them.\r\n\r\nFrom an early age, gaming wasn\'t just a hobby for me. It was a way to connect, to compete, and to express something bigger than myself. While others saw it as a pastime, I saw it as a path. That vision led to the formation of Nebula Gaming — a brand built on the belief that greatness doesn’t require millions of followers or flashy sponsors. It requires grit, strategy, and unity.\r\n\r\nOur early days were humble. A small group of like-minded players, long practice sessions, and late-night Discord calls — but from day one, we had one goal: to build something that lasts. Nebula isn’t just a name. It represents something cosmic, something vast and full of potential — a reminder that from the darkest parts of the universe, stars are born.\r\n\r\nToday, Nebula Gaming is growing. We’re assembling a roster of hungry, talented players ready to make a mark. We’re competing, we’re creating, and most importantly — we’re building a community that supports each other beyond the game.\r\n\r\nOur future is clear. We aim to compete on the highest stages of eSports, to host community tournaments, to partner with passionate brands, and to keep inspiring the next generation of players — just like the pros once inspired me.\r\n\r\nThis is only the beginning. Join us, support us, or compete against us — one thing’s for sure: you’ll remember the name Nebula Gaming.'),
