(480, 103, 'content_left', '<strong>\"Nebula Gaming: Beyond Competition\"</strong>\r\n\r\nAt Nebula Gaming, we\'re not just another eSports team — we\'re a collective of visionaries, strategists, and relentless competitors who redefine what it means to win. Founded on the belief that gaming is an art and competition a science, our journey is fueled by innovation, unity, and unmatched skill. Whether on the digital battlefield or behind the scenes, our focus remains the same: excellence, always.'),
(481, 103, '_content_left', 'field_6808b8c5350be'),
(482, 103, 'content_right', '<strong>\"The Future is Nebula\"</strong>\r\n\r\nWith rising stars across multiple titles and an ever-growing fanbase, Nebula Gaming is more than a team — it\'s a movement. We\'re expanding our roster, investing in technology, and building a community that celebrates passion and performance. Join us as we take competitive gaming to the stratosphere and beyond.'),
(483, 103, '_content_right', 'field_6808bb049e7c3'),
(484, 103, 'content_bottom', '<strong>\"United by Skill. Driven by Legacy.\"</strong>\r\n\r\nIn the ever-evolving universe of eSports, one constant remains: greatness is earned, not given. At Nebula Gaming, we’re crafting more than just championship teams — we’re building a legacy brick by brick, round by round. Our players train with discipline, compete with purpose, and represent something bigger than themselves.\r\n\r\nWe believe in the grind — the long hours, the failed attempts, the comeback moments that define true competitors. Behind every highlight reel is a squad that bleeds strategy, breathes synergy, and never backs down from the fight. We’re not here to chase trends. We’re here to set them.\r\n\r\nBut Nebula Gaming is more than what happens in-game. We’re a growing community of creators, fans, streamers, analysts, and dreamers. We collaborate, compete, and celebrate the journey together. Whether you\'re grinding in ranked, screaming on LAN, or just watching from the sidelines — if you’ve got the fire, you’re one of us.\r\n\r\nThe galaxy is vast, but our direction is clear: forward. And with every win, every fan, and every step, we get closer to becoming a name that echoes across the stars of the eSports cosmos.'),
(485, 103, '_content_bottom', 'field_6808de7710e71'),
(486, 103, 'content_top', '\"At Nebula Gaming, we\'re not just building a team — we\'re shaping a legacy. Fueled by precision, strategy, and relentless passion, we rise above the competition to redefine what it means to play at the highest level. Whether on the battlefield or behind the scenes, our mission remains the same: to inspire, to dominate, and to evolve. Welcome to the next generation of eSports.\"'),
